The paper discusses the recent progress in AI, particularly in vision, language, control, and decision-making, which are all subfields of AI covered by the arXiv categories cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.RO, and cs.AI. The paper also emphasizes the importance of structured representations and computations, which are relevant to the arXiv categories cs.LG and cs.NE. Finally, the paper introduces a new building block for the AI toolkit, the graph network, which is relevant to the arXiv category cs.AI.
